    "Finally, based on k classification results, each record is voted on to determine its final classification.",
    "The schematic diagram is shown in Fig. 7.",
    "Simply put, Random Forest consists of multiple decision trees and is a comprehensive learning model.",
    "When a new classification is initiated, specific attributes of the object are chosen as the standard.",
    "All decision trees in RF will make their own decision, and then \"vote\" collectively."
